# UPDD .gitignore (created 2026-05-05, Phase 2 of code unification)

# AmberTools MMPBSA.py transient scratch (regenerable)
# These files are written by MMPBSA.py to its CWD; if MMPBSA.py is launched
# from repo root they pollute the working tree. Pattern is conservative
# enough to not match any tracked .md / .py / .json paths.
_MMPBSA_*
mdout
*.mdcrd.0

